      <scopecontent id="aspace_dcc237449e870a86f5bb7256d196c75c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection is comprised of peace rally handouts, newsclippings, related third party materials, and correspondence of the New Haven Peace Coalition, a local grass-roots effort, begun to protest the Gulf War, 1990-1991, and later the Second Gulf War and related conflicts.  Also included are materials related to the Connecticut Peace Coalition, a broader effort of the New Haven Peace Coalition, and the national Iraq Pledge of Resistance, 2003.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
